<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><record_update table="sys_script_include"><sys_script_include action="INSERT_OR_UPDATE"><access>package_private</access><active>true</active><api_name>x_ibmj_mgr_spt.getManagerTaskDefaultValue</api_name><caller_access/><client_callable>true</client_callable><description/><name>getManagerTaskDefaultValue</name><script><![CDATA[var getManagerTaskDefaultValue = Class.create();
getManagerTaskDefaultValue.prototype = Object.extendsObject(global.AbstractAjaxProcessor, {
	getValue: function(){
		var mngTaskKey = this.getParameter('sysparm_sys_id');
		var cObj = {};
		var gr = new GlideRecord('x_ibmj_mgr_spt_manager_task');
		gr.addQuery('sys_id', mngTaskKey);
		gr.query();
		gr.next();
		cObj.u_parent_taskmaster = gr.getValue('u_parent_taskmaster');
		cObj.u_requester = gr.getValue('u_requester');
		cObj.u_task_detail = gr.getValue('u_task_detail');
		cObj.u_task_comment = gr.getValue('u_task_comment');
		cObj.u_nomination_slot = gr.getValue('u_nomination_slot');
		cObj.u_task_due_date = gr.getValue('u_task_due_date');
		return JSON.stringify(cObj);
	},
    type: 'getManagerTaskDefaultValue'
});]]></script><sys_class_name>sys_script_include</sys_class_name><sys_created_by>GaoTang.Xiong</sys_created_by><sys_created_on>2020-05-07 03:02:33</sys_created_on><sys_id>373d8e361ba0d410d16d8735cc4bcbaf</sys_id><sys_mod_count>0</sys_mod_count><sys_name>getManagerTaskDefaultValue</sys_name><sys_package display_value="Manager Support" source="x_ibmj_mgr_spt">5284b0151b449410cbd3ece9bc4bcb11</sys_package><sys_policy>read</sys_policy><sys_scope display_value="Manager Support">5284b0151b449410cbd3ece9bc4bcb11</sys_scope><sys_update_name>sys_script_include_373d8e361ba0d410d16d8735cc4bcbaf</sys_update_name><sys_updated_by>GaoTang.Xiong</sys_updated_by><sys_updated_on>2020-05-07 03:02:33</sys_updated_on></sys_script_include></record_update>
